21T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"呢個係緣份<br />\n去行山有隻貓自己跟住人行，咁就帶左佢返黎啦<br />\n又瘦又病，睇醫生都駛左我幾千蚊<br />\n不過而家好有精力好生猛"},{"pid":"442b94a0ee189fc960bb30a1ca5b5c1fefa87949","tid":990224,"uid":11929,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"執貓=偷貓<br />\n你點知執到既貓貓有冇主人？<br />\n執到記住上網問下有冇人走失貓先養"},{"pid":"2e0e22449b5e5c638315de8d19c788fd840906e2","tid":990224,"uid":83759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"如果真係捉 你要捉完即刻帶佢睇獸醫 唔好心急帶返屋企 <br />\n啲蝨多到嚇死人<br />\n杜蟲 全身檢查 打針 洗唔少錢 最好留醫幾日先 接個時就會全新乾淨貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過獸醫睇得出執返黎 多數有折 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾千走唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果剪左耳就唔好帶返屋企 多數成體貓 流浪左一段時間<br />\n大多數個體唔習慣家居環境 除時自己走佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非見到有病受左傷就無計啦 <br />\n如果見到大媽餵開 同大媽傾下計 了解下附近流浪貓<br />\n大媽最熟悉邊啲新黎 怕人 邊隻有BB"},{"pid":"87eb0758435d99ab6454392d298312a9efa496d7","tid":990224,"uid":4336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"認真答你  九龍公園 早上0600-0700  或者晚上2200 後 <br />\n個度好快變成貓公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576a9a961d36f86637e15f0492b40c488ba9f1cb","tid":990224,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"有無人想養貓？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/990012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/990012</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n隔離post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11acc743e898ad4d4c33d73c6fa411439f97a4fd","tid":990224,"uid":200596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576a9a961d36f86637e15f0492b40c488ba9f1cb","tid":990224,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"有無人想養貓？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/990012\" data-auto-